OL,6,FA motorist who ignored warnings his
OL,7,Feyesight was not good enough to drive,
OL,8,Fhas been jailed after he knocked down
OL,9,Fand killed two women in Southport.
OL,11,FGlyn Jones, 68, was told by his
OL,12,Foptician and GP on several occasions
OL,13,Fthat his vision was well below the
OL,14,Fstandard required for driving a
OL,15,Fvehicle but he did not inform the DVLA
OL,16,For insurers.
