OL,3,CLanchashire driver who ignored sight
OL,4,Cwarnings , jailed for killing friends
OL,6,FJones from Blackgate Lane in Tarleton
OL,7,Fwas driving his Audi A3 when he hit
OL,8,Ffriends Marie Cunningham, 79, and
OL,9,FGrace Foulds, 85, as they crossed the
OL,10,Froad in Southport, Merseyside, on
OL,11,FNovember 30 2021. He later failed a
OL,12,Froadside eye test.
OL,14,FBoth pensioners were taken to hospital
OL,15,Ffrom the scene in Lulworth Road, but
OL,16,Fdied in hospital from multiple
OL,17,Fcatastrophic injuries.
OL,19,FJones was sentenced at Liverpool Crown
OL,20,FCourt to seven years and four months
OL,21,Fin jail, said Merseyside Police.
