OL,6,FHe was also banned from driving for
OL,7,Fnine years and 10 months after he
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty at an earlier hearing
OL,9,Fto two counts of causing death by
OL,10,Fdangerous driving, police added.
OL,12,FThe court heard that Jones suffers
OL,13,Ffrom a "progressive condition",
OL,14,Fadvanced keratoconus, in both eyes
OL,15,Fwhich was "first diagnosed in excess
OL,16,Fof 10 years prior" to his most recent
OL,17,Fexamination in July 2019. Despite
OL,18,Fthis, he told Merseyside Police that
OL,19,Fhe had had his eyes tested in
OL,20,FSeptember 2021 and "there had been no
OL,21,Fissues".
