OL,6,FIn a statement issued through police,
OL,7,FMs Cunningham's family said: "On the
OL,8,F30th November 2021 we lost a woman
OL,9,Fthat cared more about helping her
OL,10,Ffriend across the road than getting
OL,11,Fherself home. Doing what she did best,
OL,12,Fhelping others."
OL,14,F"Over the last two years, we have
OL,15,Flived and breathed the trauma, grief,
OL,16,Ffrustration, anxiety, but most of all,
OL,17,Fthe sadness and loss of our beautiful
OL,18,Fmum."
