OL,7,Fcomplicated investigation involving
OL,8,Fanalysis of the eyesight records of Mr
OL,9,FJones by an expert optometrist, who
OL,10,Fconcluded his eyesight was not fit for
OL,11,Fdriving, indeed it was so bad he would
OL,12,Fnot have been able to see the steering
OL,13,Fwheel.
